          Dad, we don’t think of you as gone away</br>
          As your journey’s just begun,</br>
          Life holds so many facets</br>
          This earth is only one.</br> </br>
          
          We just think of you as resting</br>
          In a place of warmth and comfort</br>
          Where there are no days and years</br>
          And not even sadness and tears.</br> </br>
          
          Dad you were always kind and caring</br>
          And so understanding too</br>
          And if help was ever needed Dad</br>
          It always came from you.</br>
      </div>
      
