      </div>
      
      
      <div class="poem col-md-3">
          How we wish that you could know today</br>
          How great is our sadness</br>
          That you have passed away.</br> </br>
          
          We will always think of you as living</br>
          In the hearts of those you touched</br>
          For nothing loved is ever lost</br>
          And you were loved so much.</br> </br>
          
          So rest in peace dearest Dad</br>
          And thank you for all you’ve done</br>
          As we pray to God to give you</br>
